                  li #[a(href="https://www.datacamp.com/blog/claude-artifacts-introduction") Claude Artifacts 101 (DataCamp)] - Types, use cases, sharing
                  li #[a(href="https://simonwillison.net/2024/Oct/21/claude-artifacts/") Everything I built with Claude Artifacts (Simon Willison)] - Real-world examples
                  li #[a(href="https://christinasouch.com/blog/fixing-claude-artifact-creation-issues") Fixing Claude Artifact Issues] - Troubleshooting common problems
